Package: data.texas.gov
Title: Texas Open Data (Socrata SODA) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Texas Open Data Socrata SODA API.
    Covers dataset listing, SoQL queries, and auto-paginated fetching. Includes
    LLM context injection via txgov_context().
